{
  "chapter": 238,
  "chapter_summary": "第二百三十八章 禁宫畅叙。项少龙潜入魏王宫后宫，藏身于单美美寝宫附近。两名宫娥在膳房议论单美美心情不佳，项少龙趁机取得糕点跟踪至前进大厅。他翻入单美美侧厅，趁其未归先入寝室搜寻地道入口。单美美回房后发现项少龙藏于屏风后，两人在绣榻上亲密交谈。单美美坦言对项少龙心存感激与爱慕，项少龙则坦陈身陷险境无暇儿女情长。单美美告知寝室内确有地道可通城外，但钥匙在内侍长手上。项少龙凭开锁技艺可自行开启。单美美提及姊妹凤菲将赴齐国贺寿，项少龙不愿牵累他人。单美美不舍项少龙离去，两人温存一番后，项少龙决定趁大雪夜从地道脱身。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_e_jia",
      "speaker_name": "宫娥甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她的心情定是非常不好，我还是首次见她骂人骂得这么凶哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_e_yi",
      "speaker_name": "宫娥乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要乱说话，给那些爱搬弄是非的小人听到就糟糕了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiu_ju",
      "speaker_name": "秀菊",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "娘娘！不要担心吧！项爷吉人天相，他又那么本事，自有脱身之法。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiu_ju",
      "text": "担心有什么用？秀菊，我不要房间这么光亮。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiu_ju",
      "speaker_name": "秀菊",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "大王今晚怕不会来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiu_ju",
      "text": "现在他只想得到项少龙的人头，怎还有闲心到这里来，夜了！你回去睡吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "美美可是受惊了？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你要人家怎样帮你呢？唉！项爷真是神通广大，竟有办法来到这里找人家。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "美美到屏风后去不是要……嘿……",
      "tone": "尴尬",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好了，终可以和你睡在一块儿。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "美美真的垂青于我吗？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我是很易钟情于有本领的男人，不过很快又会厌倦，但对你确有些不同。你该知在目前的情况下，我再不必口不对心。初时我很恨你，你这人哩！总不肯把人放在眼里，想不到杨豫姊真没说错，你这人是外冷内热，只有你才肯那样帮我的大忙。人家尚未有机会亲口谢你哩！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "你刚才不是'亲口'谢了我吗？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你对我没有兴趣吗？为何毫无反应呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "一来我觉得美美你已是有主名花，不该侵犯。最重要是现在身陷险境，正忧心如何离开，所以难以放开怀抱，和美美你享受鱼水之欢。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你既能来，自然也有本事离开吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你既然找到我门上来，我自然也要把你安全送走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "这样你可太危险了，而且有太多不可测知的变量在内，我绝不能让你冒这个险。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "世上恐怕只有项少龙肯这么为人设想。项少龙啊！快想想办法吧！只要我单美美办得到的，我就肯去为你办。",
      "tone": "感动",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "你大王有没有告诉你后宫内有逃离王城的地道？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我差点忘了！确有这么一条地道，就在寝室内。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "但开锁的钥匙却掌管在内侍长手上，我打不开来哩！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "那就更好，就算我走后给人发觉，你也可推个一干二净。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你懂得开锁吗？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "你知否地道的出口在哪里呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大王说地道的出口在离东城城门不远一个养马厩的天井处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "后悔吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我不知道！真的不知道！昨晚我梦见醉风楼，和豫姊像往常般在花园里玩抛球，唉！她们怎样了？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "他对你好吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我真的弄不清楚，自登上王位后，他变得很厉害，有时梦中也会叫着要杀某个开罪了他的大臣的名字。若非人家有身孕，说不定会央你带我走呢！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "你刚才去见的姊妹，是否三大名姬之首的凤菲？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是的！我们还曾说起你来，她很欣赏你哩！不若求她掩护你出城好吗？她是很有办法的人。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "不！我不想牵累任何人，她为何要到齐国去？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是为了齐王的五十大寿，听说石素芳和兰宫媛都应邀到那里去。包括秦国在内，各国均会派代表去贺寿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "燕、赵两国不是和齐国交战吗？为何忽然和好起来？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "对这种事我不大清楚。听大王说，好像齐王到现在仍决定不了谁当太子，其中牵涉到田单的权力，所以大王很热中于齐国太子策立的问题。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "乖美美！快告诉我地道的入口在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要那么快走好吗？我有办法把你藏上几天哩！待风头火势过后再走，不是更安全吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "不！我定要趁现在大雪时走，雪停后更走不了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "搂着你，就像把往昔最可贵的全拥有了，你却那么不停嚷着要走，项少龙啊！不要对人家那么无情好吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "我怎舍得无情待你呢？不过我现在须保留体力，以应付艰苦的逃亡生涯。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我不再逼你了，但你总该有点表示，例如摸摸人家的身体，那将来就不致会轻易忘掉美美。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "地道入口在大衣柜里，下面是块活板，揭起它可见到锁死了的地道入口。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "究竟有没有别的入口？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "御园内有两个入口，宫内的人都知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "那就更好，因入口既多，我走后纵使给人发觉，仍不会怀疑到你头上来。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 238,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    }
  ],
